5\">25</sup>For I am the <span class=\"nd\">Lord</span>; I will speak the word that I will speak, and it will be performed. It will no longer be delayed, but in your days, O rebellious house, I will speak the word and perform it, declares the Lord <span class=\"nd\">God</span>.\u201d</span></p>\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"v26_12_26\"><sup id=\"Ezek.12.26\" class=\"v26_12_26\">26</sup>And the word of the <span class=\"nd\">Lord</span> came to me: </span><span class=\"v26_12_27\"><sup id=\"Ezek.12.27\" class=\"v26_12_27\">27</sup>\u201cSon of man, behold, they of the house of Israel say, \u2018The vision that he sees is for many days from now, and he prophesies of times far off.\u2019 </span><span class=\"v26_12_28\"><sup id=\"Ezek.12.28\" class=\"v26_12_28\">28</sup>Therefore say to them, Thus says the Lord <span class=\"nd\">God</span>: None of my words will be delayed any longer, but the word that I speak will be performed, declares the Lord <span class=\"nd\">God</span>.\u201d</span></p>\n</div>\n", 
