ill require at your hand. </span><span class=\"v26_33_9\"><sup id=\"Ezek.33.9\" class=\"v26_33_9\">9</sup>But if you warn the wicked to turn from his way, and he does not turn from his way, that person shall die in his iniquity, but you will have delivered your soul.</span></p>\n<h3 class=\"s1\">Why Will You Die, Israel?</h3>\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"v26_33_10\"><sup id=\"Ezek.33.10\" class=\"v26_33_10\">10</sup>\u201cAnd you, son of man, say to the house of Israel, Thus have you said: \u2018Surely our transgressions and our sins are upon us, and we rot away because of them. How then can we live?\u2019 </span><span class=\"v26_33_11\"><sup id=\"Ezek.33.11\" class=\"v26_33_11\">11</sup>Say to them, As I live, declares the Lord <span class=\"nd\">God</span>, I have no pleasure in the death of the wicked, but that the wicked turn from his way and live; turn back, turn back from your evil ways, for why will you die, O house of Israel?</span></p>\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"v26_33_12\"><sup id=\"Ezek.33.12\" class=\"v26_33_12\">12</sup>\u201cAnd you, son of man, say to your people, The righteousness of the righteous shall not deliver him when he transgresses, and as for the wickedness of the wicked, he shall not fall by it when he turns from his wickedness, and the righteous shall not be able to live by his righteousness when he sins. </span><span class=\"v26_33_13\"><sup id=\"Ezek.33.13\" class=\"v26_33_13\">13</sup>Though I say to the righteous that he shall surely live, yet if he trusts in his righteousness and does injustice, none of his righteous deeds shall be remembered, but in his injustice that he has done he shall die. </span><span class=\"v26_33_14\"><sup id=\"Ezek.33.14\" class=\"v26_33_14\">14</sup>Again, though I say to the wicked, \u2018You shall surely die,\u2019 yet if he turns from his sin and does what is just and right, </span><span class=\"v26_33_15\"><sup id=\"Ezek.33.15\" class=\"v26_33_15\">15</sup>if the wicked restores the pledge, gives b